{"tid":2123859,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣電總局下令播抗美援朝劇洗腦","createTime":"2020-07-25T03:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T04:05:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"247184fc43e182b11337a2be8f584aa125d0becb","tid":2123859,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200725/F65IZDB55PUZVQGPAA5TLX5EFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2FF65IZDB55PUZVQGPAA5TLX5EFY%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxdgc6rz%2Ba6PLwHdujBQ9FQE%3D&h=5a8498e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2FF65IZDB55PUZVQGPAA5TLX5EFY%2F&h=80050eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200725/F65IZDB55PUZVQGPAA5TLX5EFY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n廣電總局下令播抗美援朝劇洗腦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eW3tTbWUAzYHJa1rP9S8wfEUi2E=/765x531/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I5SBKPD4IAW75U34NLTCO42CWE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeW3tTbWUAzYHJa1rP9S8wfEUi2E%3D%2F765x531%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI5SBKPD4IAW75U34NLTCO42CWE.gif&h=0af7fa42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地有不少電視劇以韓戰為題材。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n武肺疫情蔓延全球，加上中美關係持續緊張，廣電總局近日召開全國廣電系統電視電話會議，部署播出抗戰、抗美援朝（韓戰）、抗疫題材電視劇，強調需弘揚抗戰和抗美援朝精神，以及「講好抗擊新冠肺炎疫情中國行動的感人故事。」有網民慨嘆：「強行洗腦國人！」<br />\n<br />\n廣電總局電視劇司在23日召開全國廣電系統視訊會議，。。。。。。。。。。。。三年韓戰，中方15萬人戰死，22萬人傷。<br />\n<br />\n針對紀念抗戰勝利75周年電視劇的播出安排，廣電總局近日發出通知，要求相關播放機構不得播出違背常識常理、隨意戲說解讀歷史、過度娛樂化的抗戰題材電視劇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n籌備新劇歌頌建黨百年<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：現場聽演說 王丹：如宣佈冷戰開始<br />\n<br />\n2021年是中共建黨100周年，廣電總局網站還發佈，16日已召開電視劇「理想照耀中國」創作論證會，指這齣戲透過40個黨員故事，闡釋「中國共產黨為甚麼能」。<br />\n<br />\n中新社"},{"pid":"02e9496bffb012320e9e6fcc9355f3be0d